    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Wish somebody'd speak straight for once, okay?",
    "start": 30.735,
    "end": 33.82,
    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Talking circles like a worn-out tire,",
