    "end": 57.82,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady laughs soft with a subtle rebound.",
    "start": 57.82,
    "end": 61.592,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "They spotted a footprint—nah, not factual,",
