    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "How to keep every angle harder to peel.",
    "start": 77.363,
    "end": 80.106,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Host says evidence always tells what's real…",
    "start": 80.106,
    "end": 82.849,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Cut to me scribbling notes during every ordeal.",
    "start": 82.849,
    "end": 85.592,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Neighbors whisper like they're part of a cast,",
    "start": 86.62,
    "end": 89.363,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Claiming my movement's a little too fast.",
    "start": 89.363,
    "end": 92.106,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Narrator pops in: “That theory won't last.”",
    "start": 92.106,
    "end": 94.849,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Fade to black—jump cut—back to the task.",
    "start": 94.849,
    "end": 97.592,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
