    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Filling each moment with sarcastic shape.",
    "start": 101.363,
    "end": 104.106,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Drama in the room that nobody escapes,",
    "start": 104.106,
    "end": 106.849,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing here follows the usual way.",
    "start": 106.849,
    "end": 109.592,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "We go round and round…",
